sequenceDiagram
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant CI as CI Runner
    participant Registry as Container Registry
    participant ArgoCD as ArgoCD
    participant K8s as Kubernetes
    participant Slack as Slack

    Dev->>GH: git push (feature branch)
    GH->>CI: webhook: push event
    CI->>CI: Install dependencies
    CI->>CI: Run lint + unit tests
    alt Tests Fail
        CI-->>GH: ❌ status check failed
        CI->>Slack: "Build failed on feature/xyz"
        GH-->>Dev: PR blocked
    else Tests Pass
        CI->>CI: Build container image
        CI->>CI: Run security scan (Trivy)
        CI->>Registry: docker push app:sha-abc123
        CI-->>GH: ✅ all checks passed
    end

    Dev->>GH: Merge PR to main
    GH->>CI: webhook: merge event
    CI->>CI: Build production image
    CI->>Registry: docker push app:v1.2.3
    CI->>GH: Update k8s/deployment.yaml (image tag)
    GH-->>ArgoCD: GitOps sync detected
    ArgoCD->>K8s: kubectl apply (rolling update)
    K8s->>K8s: Rolling restart pods
    K8s-->>ArgoCD: Deployment healthy
    ArgoCD->>Slack: "v1.2.3 deployed to production ✅"
    Slack-->>Dev: Deployment notification
